definition: car door/door of bus, railway carriage etc
car/vehicle/CL:輛|辆[liang4]/machine/to shape with a lathe/Kangxi radical 159

gate/door/CL:扇[shan4]/gateway/doorway/CL:個|个[ge4]/opening/valve/switch/way to do something/knack/family/house/(religious) sect/school (of thought)/class/category/phylum or division (taxonomy)/classifier for large guns/classifier for lessons, subjects, branches of technology/(suffix) -gate (i.e. scandal; derived from Watergate)

sentences.english: They opened the door and the four men alighted .
sentences.chinese: 他们打开车门，四个人都走了出来。

sentences.english: Step 6: If you cannot open the doors, look for an emergency exit window.
sentences.chinese: 如果无法打开紧急车门，则寻找太平门窗户。

sentences.english: Both doors were open and snow was fast covering the car.
sentences.chinese: 车门都开着，大雪迅速的盖住了车。

sentences.english: He leans his arms on the door and brings his face to the window.
sentences.chinese: 他把胳膊枕在车门上，把脸凑近窗户。

sentences.english: She got out of the car and slammed the door.
sentences.chinese: 她下了车，车门“哐当”一声关了。

sentences.english: He quickly opens the door and fumbles an arm and pulls it hard.
sentences.chinese: 他赶紧打开车门，摸到一只手臂，使劲拽。

sentences.english: Shoot! My coat is caught in the door.
This front door shell applies to hover , quality and cheap , welcomed to order .
sentences.chinese: 此车门适用于长城哈弗车系，质优价廉，欢迎订购。

sentences.english: The director opened her door and got out.
sentences.chinese: 理事长打开车门下了车。

sentences.english: Aziraphale blinked, lowered his hands, and gingerly opened the door.
sentences.chinese: 亚茨拉斐尔眨眨眼，放下手，小心翼翼的打开车门。

sentences.english: A man in a black coat opened the door of the car and got in.
sentences.chinese: 一个穿黑大衣的男人打开车门，钻了进来。

sentences.english: Hit the road in this sporty green street machine with opening doors.
sentences.chinese: 打开车门，让此款花俏的绿色道路机器冲向道路中。

sentences.english: Install the screws attaching the mirror to the door.
sentences.chinese: 安装把视镜固定在车门上的螺丝。

sentences.english: It was empty and the door was smeared with blood.
sentences.chinese: 那校车早已空了，车门上染满了血污。

sentences.english: Releasing wiring harness from the basic door frame .
sentences.chinese: 松开基本车门框架的线束。

sentences.english: I threw up all over your door.
sentences.chinese: 我呕吐到你的车门上了。
